{{SupportPage|vendor=Linksys|model=BEFW11S4}} There are two FCC IDs for the BEFW11S4 v2, MXF-C901114 ([[Gemtek WL-375]], PRISM 2.5) and MXF-C910308 ([[Gemtek WL-375P]], PRISM 3). Some units list the FCC ID as just MXF-C901114 (see [http://www.squakmt.com/LinksysBEFW11S4.V2/ here]) while others list both (see [http://gallery.cdk.com/linksys?page=1 here]). It is not known if the units which list both FCC IDs consist of a mix of both parts or are strictly the newer WL-375Ps. It is also not known if there is a version listing strictly the newer FCC ID (v2.1?). CPU is part no. 3C4510B01-QERO / 3C4510B01-QER0.
